  <brief_title>A Prospective Cohort Study of Perioperative Covert Stroke and Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Cohort Study of Perioperative Covert Stroke and Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction in Elderly Patients Undergoing Noncardiac Surgery</official_title>
